216	// Plugin config
217	// ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
218	
219	// No config knobs in MVP — postgres + kysely come from the
220	// @ax/database-postgres service via the bus. Knobs may land alongside
221	// Task 14 (e.g. soft-delete retention window) but only if a second
222	// backend would also want them. We keep the type so the public surface
